			<div class="container">
				<h1 class="section-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
				
				<div class="privacy-content">
					<p class="intro-text">
						Welcome to Phoenixx Casino Goa ("Casino," "we," "us," or "our"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, 
