								<li>Process transactions and maintain gaming records.</li>
								<li>Improve website functionality and user experience.</li>
								<li>Provide customer support and respond to inquiries.</li>
								<li>Send promotional offers, updates, and event notifications (if opted in).</li>
								<li>Ensure responsible gambling practices and detect fraud or suspicious activities.</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="privacy-item">
						<h2 class="privacy-heading">3. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
						<div class="privacy-details">
