							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="privacy-item">
						<h2 class="privacy-heading">4. Data Security</h2>
						<div class="privacy-details">
							<p>We implement strict security measures to protect your personal data, including encryption, access control, and regular security audits. However, no online platform is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="privacy-item">
						<h2 class="privacy-heading">5. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
						<div class="privacy-details">
							<p>We use cookies and similar technologies to:</p>
							<ul>
								<li>Enhance website performance and functionality.</li>
								<li>Analyze user behavior to improve our services.</li>
								<li>Provide personalized marketing content.</li>
							</ul>
							<p>You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="privacy-item">
						<h2 class="privacy-heading">6. Your Rights</h2>
						<div class="privacy-details">
							<p>You have the right to:</p>
							<ul>
								<li>Access, update, or correct your personal data.</li>
								<li>Opt out of marketing communications at any time.</li>
								<li>Request deletion of your data (subject to legal and regulatory requirements).</li>
							</ul>
							<p>To exercise these rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:marketing@phoenixcasino.in" class="link">marketing@phoenixcasino.in</a>.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="privacy-item">
